info.name: Oyikio
info.description:
# Introduction
This repository contains the source code of the api services. In this file the api interface and sample endpoints will be given.

# Overview
Don't forget to use api keys given in GitLab readme.md
# Authentication
API-KEYs put in the request header, X-API-KEY

# Error Codes
Error codes 400, 401, 404, 408, 424, 500, and 503 are returned in some cases. However the error code use is not consistent (standardized) -yet. So it is possible to get an error code instead of another, more appropriate, error code. Or even getting successful response 200 when there actually an error occured. Don't be *fully* relied on the http status codes of response.
